    <item>
      <title>Version 3.2.0</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 09:47:24 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>8</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>Complete UI redesign with a new menu bar popover, main window, and slide-down settings drawer.</li><li>Ten selectable themes: System (follows macOS light/dark), Hoth, Risa, Weasley, Starbuck, Cylon, Vader, Kirk, Hermione, and Nerds.</li><li>Friendly account names (Work, Personal, Family) that show everywhere in place of the raw email address.</li><li>Menu bar popover shows recent unread messages collapsed under each account; click the chevron to unfurl.</li><li>Gmail and Outlook brand icons next to every account.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
      <enclosure
        url="https://pub-9c8d72fe664b4ce18aac0d718b4e0346.r2.dev/apps/mail-notifier/MailNotifier-3.2.0.dmg"
